OL,3,CJail for knife-wielding man who was
OL,4,Ctackled to the floor by shoppers
OL,6,FA man who was tackled to the ground by
OL,7,Fbrave members of the public after he
OL,8,Fstabbed someone four times in Bristol
OL,9,Fcity centre has been jailed for six
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FIan McInally, of Talbot Avenue in St
OL,13,FGeorge, appeared at Bristol Crown
OL,14,FCourt on Monday 29 July.
OL,16,FHe had previously admitted to causing
OL,17,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent and
OL,18,Fbeing in possession of a bladed
OL,19,Farticle in a public place.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
