OL,3,CJail for knife-wielding man who was
OL,4,Ctackled to the floor by shoppers
OL,6,FOfficers arrived at the scene within
OL,7,Ftwo minutes of the initial call and
OL,8,Farrested 37-year-old McInally.
OL,10,FThe victim was taken to Southmead
OL,11,FHospital and received emergency
OL,12,Ftreatment for stab wounds and a
OL,13,Ffractured jaw, before he was
OL,14,Fdischarged to recover at home a week
OL,15,Flater.
OL,17,FDC Spicer added: "This was a horrible
OL,18,Fincident during a busy time of day
OL,19,Fwhen families were walking in the
OL,20,Farea, going about their day.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
