OL,3,CJail for knife-wielding man who was
OL,4,Ctackled to the floor by shoppers
OL,6,F"Such an act of violence will not be
OL,7,Ftolerated and we remain dedicated to
OL,8,Fcracking down on knife crime and
OL,9,Fviolent crime in our communities."
OL,11,FMcInally was handed a four-year and
OL,12,Ffour-month sentence for the GBH
OL,13,Foffences, with a 12-month sentence for
OL,14,Fthe possession of a bladed article in
OL,15,Fa public place charge to run
OL,16,Fconcurrently.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
