OL,3,CJail for knife-wielding man who was
OL,4,Ctackled to the floor by shoppers
OL,6,FHis actions also activated a suspended
OL,7,Fsentence for a robbery from August
OL,8,Flast year, which saw the judge, HHJ
OL,9,FCullum, add an additional 20-month-
OL,10,Fterm to his sentence to run
OL,11,Fconsecutively.
OL,13,FIn total, he was sentenced to six
OL,14,Fyears in jail with an additional three
OL,15,Fyears on extended licence.
OL,17,FIn his sentencing, HHJ Cullum,
OL,18,Fdescribed the impact of the physical
OL,19,Feffects the injuries had on the
OL,20,Fvictim, stating they were "clearly
OL,21,Flife-threatening".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
