OL,6,FHe added: "(The victim) was not a
OL,7,Fthreat to you, you carried and knife
OL,8,Fand you showed aggressive behaviour
OL,9,Fand went after him.
OL,11,F"You carried on the assault until you
OL,12,Fwere taken down and, while not a
OL,13,Fparticularly long assault, it was in
OL,14,Fpartial terms a persistent assault
OL,15,Fwith a highly dangerous weapon."
